1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,920
Through the archaeological objects displayed in the pavilions, it is confirmed that our

2
00:00:04,920 --> 00:00:10,320
land has been inhabited by the Illyrians, our predecessors, and the Albanians in continuity

3
00:00:10,320 --> 00:00:13,920
as early back as four thousand years ago.

4
00:00:13,920 --> 00:00:21,540
The exhibited archaeological objects are authentic-like arms, ceramics, and bronze decorating objects.

5
00:00:21,540 --> 00:00:26,320
Since antiquity, our land was a target of various invasions and was attacked by Romans

6
00:00:26,320 --> 00:00:33,160
and after three Illyrian-Roman wars, the country was invaded by them in the year 168 BC.

7
00:00:33,160 --> 00:00:39,000
Nevertheless, neither the Roman invasion nor the Slavic eruption in the sixth century couldn't

8
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:42,080
assimilate the native population.

9
00:00:42,080 --> 00:00:47,060
This phenomenon is an example of the ethnocultural resistance of the Albanian people who founded

10
00:00:47,060 --> 00:00:50,560
the first state of Arbor in 1190.

11
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:55,400
In the antiquity pavilion are displayed the following objects.

12
00:00:55,400 --> 00:01:00,600
Objects of pre-Civic Illyrian age, 8th until 6th century BC.

13
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:06,120
Civic Illyrian cultural objects, 4th until 3rd century BC.

14
00:01:06,120 --> 00:01:08,600
Model of Libernship.

15
00:01:08,600 --> 00:01:13,060
Illyrian ceramics, 3rd until 1st century BC.

16
00:01:13,060 --> 00:01:17,080
Illyrian coins, 3rd until 2nd century BC.

17
00:01:17,080 --> 00:01:23,120
The antique city of Albanopolis and some archaeological objects about its soil.

18
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:25,120
Statue of Artemis.

19
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:27,160
Illyrian arms.

20
00:01:27,160 --> 00:01:29,160
Pyrrho, Tuta.

21
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:31,160
Illyrian-Roman wars.

22
00:01:31,160 --> 00:01:34,160
Ceramics from the Middle Ages.

23
00:01:34,160 --> 00:01:37,160
Emblem of Arbor princedom.

24
00:01:37,160 --> 00:01:39,160
Map of Arbor princedom.

